524
00:33:57.680 --> 00:33:59.661
D'accord, Ben.

525
00:33:59.765 --> 00:34:01.851
Allez, viens.

526
00:34:12.277 --> 00:34:14.363
Vire le chien.

527
00:34:16.448 --> 00:34:18.533
J'ai peur, Ben.

528
00:34:19.576 --> 00:34:22.912
